REQUIREMENTS/INSTALL:
 - pip install unidecode (transliteration to ascii)
 - apt-get install memcached
 - pip install python-memcached
 - easy_install pillow (DO NOT install using pip - use easy_install)
 - pip install pytz (time zone collection)
 - pip install sorl-thumbnail

 - pip install unidecode (unicode to ascii module) (install not needed, 'bundled' in sources)
 - pip install django-tastypie (also pip install django-tastypie --upgrade)

 - websockets: omnibus:
    download to <dir>: https://github.com/moccu/django-omnibus
    run in <dir>: pip install -r resources/requirements-develop.txt

AFTER INSTALL:
 - fill countries:
   ~$ python manage.py shell
   >>> from config import countries
   >>> countries.fill_countries()


